  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nSuppose you're trying to debug a transaction where a contract successfully self-destructs... well, at the moment, for the most part, you can't, but that's a separate issue (and we're not going to fix that until Ganache 7.1 is out and we've done something about #2894).\r\n\r\nBut, it's not *completely* true that you can't.  You can still step through with `;` and see *some* of the assembly state, even if it's not all there.  However, now when stepping through with `;` or `p`, you'll get an error message.\r\n\r\nWe can't at the moment actually print out all the helpful information you would get normally -- that'll have to wait -- but we could at least do something better than erroring.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nCreate a contract that can self-destruct.  Perform a transaction that makes it self-destruct.  Debug that transaction.  Type `p`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nNot an error message.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n```\r\ndebug(development:0x912b205d...)> p\r\n\r\n  No data on stack.\r\n\r\nInstructions:\r\nUncaught TypeError: Cannot read property 'toString' of undefined\r\n    at ReadStream.emit (events.js:314:20)\r\n    at ReadStream.onkeypress (readline.js:205:10)\r\n    at REPLServer.self._ttyWrite (repl.js:867:9)\r\n    at REPLServer.Interface._ttyWrite (readline.js:1003:14)\r\n    at REPLServer.Interface._line (readline.js:658:8)\r\n    at REPLServer.Interface._onLine (readline.js:329:10)\r\n    at REPLServer.EventEmitter.emit (domain.js:483:12)\r\n    at REPLServer.emit (events.js:314:20)\r\n    at REPLServer.onLine (repl.js:777:10)\r\n    at REPLServer.runBound [as eval] (domain.js:440:12)\r\n    at bound (domain.js:427:14)\r\n    at REPLServer.bound interpreterCallbackified (util.js:210:5)\r\n    at DebugInterpreter.interpreter (/home/sniffnoy/truffle/truffle/packages/core/lib/debug/interpreter.js:617:26)\r\n    at DebugPrinter.printInstruction (/home/sniffnoy/truffle/truffle/packages/core/lib/debug/printer.js:247:39)\r\n    at Object.formatCurrentInstruction (/home/sniffnoy/truffle/truffle/packages/debug-utils/index.js:535:21)\r\n    at Object.formatPC (/home/sniffnoy/truffle/truffle/packages/debug-utils/index.js:549:18)\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.25",
